HEADWORD: Onerary
<hw>On"er*a*ry</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>onerarius</ets>, fr. <ets>onus</ets>, <ets>oneris</ets>, load,
burden: cf. F. <ets>on⟦eacute⟧raire</ets>.]</ety> <def>Fitted for, or
